scene.message:
Maki: Let's hurry and find{nl}
that girl! She must be{nl}
somewhere in the school!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Why does the girl in{nl}
black target the school...{waitkey}What is there to gain by{nl}
attacking a school?{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: When are we ever gonna{nl}
be able to save the real{nl}
Sonomura...{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Does the girl in black{nl}
have Demons with her after{nl}
all, I wonder?{waitkey}{clearbox}If so, we'll need to brace{nl}
ourselves going in.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Hey, {ctl0f:1}, don't you{nl}
think it's worrying to leave{nl}
two women behind?{waitkey}If you like, I'll stay here{nl}
and protect the teachers!{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Finding the infirmary{nl}
in a place like this is{nl}
somehow a relief.{waitkey}{ret}

Agastya Tree:{nl}
Shall I inscribe{nl}
your record within me?{waitkey}{nl}
{ctl0e:0}{ret}

Ms. Natsumi: Ah, {ctl0f:1}.{nl}
What's happening right now?{waitkey}I don't know what to do{nl}
either. I'm at a loss{wait_fr:37}{nl}
right, Ms. Saeko?{waitkey}{ret}

Ms. Natsumi: I thought she'd{nl}
say something at a time like{nl}
this, but{wait_fr:48} she's as gloomy{nl}
as ever...{waitkey}{ret}

Ms. Natsumi: If you get hurt,{nl}
come to the infirmary. Now,{nl}
let me have a look at you.{waitkey}{ret}

Ms. Natsumi: There, all done.{nl}
Don't go losing to any{nl}
demons, now.{waitkey}{ret}
